b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Jasper and Postwise share a solid foundation of core features including Short Form, Templates, Tone Control. Where Jasper pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Long Form and Seo Tools and Plagiarism Check and Multilingual and Api Access and Team Collaboration and Browser Extension, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Jasper holds an overall score of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Postwise scores 6/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Postwise comes in at a lower starting price of $29/mo, while Jasper begins at $49/mo. Neither platform offers a free plan, so you will need to budget for at least the starting tier from the beginning. Be sure to take advantage of any trial periods they may offer."}]]}]
